#

Herb-Crusted Pork Tenderloin with Roasted Vegetables

$25
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

PorkMain CourseDinner

Description

A succulent pork tenderloin coated in a fragrant herb crust, served with seasonal roasted vegetables for a delightful balance of flavors.

Ingredients

  • Pork Tenderloin: 1 lb
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Fresh Rosemary: 2 tbsp, chopped
  • Fresh Thyme: 2 tbsp, chopped
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Salt: 1 tsp
  • Black Pepper: 1 tsp
  • Carrots: 2, sliced
  • Zucchini: 2, sliced
  • Bell Pepper: 1, diced
  • Onion: 1, chopped
